^-{ ^*BDeal of the Week 203 - July 31, 2000^*N }
^-
This is an unusual ^*BDeal of the Week^*N because it does not contain a deal. This week we will be presenting some bidding ideas that we hope you will find interesting. These methods could be added to just about any natural system, but they were designed with ^*B2/1 Game Force^*N in mind. Variations of the methods presented here have been used successfully by ^*BBridge Base Inc.^*N President ^*BFred Gitelman^*N in his partnerships with ^*BBrad Moss^*N, ^*BGeorge Mittelman^*N, and ^*BBridge Base Inc.^*N Vice President ^*BSheri Winestock^*N.

We tried presenting some bidding theory in one prior ^*BDeal of the Week^*N (February 14, 2000 - available through this web site) and received a fairly positive response from our readers. Please let us know your thoughts on this. Would you like to see more (or fewer) ^*BDeals of the Week^*N in which the focus is on the bidding? Please e-mail your comments to:

